org.cougaar.planning.plugin.util
Class PredicateFactory

java.lang.Object
  org.cougaar.planning.plugin.util.PredicateFactory

public class PredicateFactory
extends java.lang.Object

Not typically used factory for Predicates. Intended for use from script-based plugins. It's better usage to create your own predicates directly from your plugin.
